result.name: TamJai SamGor MiXian

reviews.text: Very buzzy because of lots of customers. Didn't really liked the atmosphere, but food was delicious. But pork sidedish had some fishy smell. Soup 1 is recommended.
Try the medium hot mala rice noodles.
Good noodles, great value. I recommend getting less noodles as it is quite a lot. The spicy chicken wings were quite bland, not very spicy.
Great vegan broth (only available after 3pm sadly), fab noodles, cheap and huge portions!
Has vegan options- just look for the Green Monday menu ;)

reviews.text: 超級好吃😋每次來香港必吃！

好食，小辣都幾辣，不過好食。通常叫炸醬，酸菜，墨演(丸)都幾好。約$50位
